# Stoney Maloney – Premium Skincare Theme

- **Liquid** – All markup and logic
- **CSS** – Custom styles (Playfair Display + Inter typography)
- **JavaScript** – Vanilla JS only
- **Design** – Bold orange (#E85D04), cream (#FDF8F3), Savor-inspired storytelling

## Brand

- Natural tallow-based skincare
- Products: Miracle Recovery Rub, Tallow Lip Balm
- Tone: Natural, healing, premium, warm
- Client assets in `client_assets/` (logo, product shots, pattern)

## Sections

Hero, What Is Tallow, Benefits, Product Showcase, Real Results, Brand Story, Ingredients, Testimonials, Retail/Events, Footer. All editable in theme editor.
